These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, march
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Birthday   | march | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, architect
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the architect##8
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the architect##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Job   | architect | accountant   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
1. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Cigar          | oliveros | ritmeester |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b     |

 #################################

 
